== 發行 ==
電影在美國發行的原始日期為2016年7月22日<ref>{{cite web|title=Paul Feig tweeted the release date|url=https://twitter.com/paulfeig/status/560238397273300992|publisher=twitter.com|date=2015-01-27|accessdate=2015-01-28|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108115525/https://twitter.com/paulfeig/status/560238397273300992|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但於2015年8月5日，日期提前至2016年7月15日<ref>{{cite web|title=Sony Slates 16 Films Including 'The Dark Tower', 'Jumanji' Reboot & Two 'Bad Boys'|url=http://deadline.com/2015/08/sony-release-dates-dark-tower-jumanji-bad-boys-3-passengers-1201492350/|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2015-08-05|accessdate=|archive-date=2021-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210409170703/https://deadline.com/2015/08/sony-release-dates-dark-tower-jumanji-bad-boys-3-passengers-1201492350/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在中國大陸，即使負責外片輸入的[[中国电影公司|中国电影公司]]方面認為觀眾對舊作陌生不會有市場、以及[[广电总局|广电总局]]禁止鬼怪出現政策下，[[索尼|索尼]]仍打算送審<ref>{{cite news |title='Ghostbusters' Denied Release in China |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ghostbusters-denied-release-china-910563 |accessdate= |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2016-07-13 |archive-date=2016-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161108091724/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ghostbusters-denied-release-china-910563 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title='Ghostbusters' Not Submitted For China Release Yet, Sony Says|url=http://deadline.com/2016/07/sony-ghostbusters-china-release-1201786088/|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2016-07-13|accessdate=|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108091733/https://deadline.com/2016/07/sony-ghostbusters-china-release-1201786088/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Sinaweibo post |user =1803310643 |id = DEJzcgasg |title =《超能敢-{}-死队》能否在中国上映成谜 |name = 守望好莱-{}-坞 |date = 2016-07-14. |accessdate = |language=}}</ref>，但最終依舊無法上映。

=== 評價 ===

《魔鬼剋星》在2016年3月在youtube釋出第一支預告片，首日觀看次數超過2400萬，隨即引發負評炸彈，至2016年5月，該預告片已成為youtube最不受歡迎電影預告第一名，及最不喜歡影片第九名，有28萬人點讚，超過百萬人點倒讚。

上映後獲得正負兩極的評價，影評人多稱讚演員的表現（尤其是[[凱特·麥金儂|麥金儂]]和[[克里斯·漢斯沃|漢斯沃]]），但批評其剪輯和步調<ref name="reviews">{{cite news |title=‘Ghostbusters’: Reviews Agree That Funny Ladies Save Uninspired Reboot |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/ghostbusters-review-round-up-paul-feig-melissa-mccarthy-kristen-wiig-1201811470/ |accessdate=2016-07-10 |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=2016-07-10 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108120210/https://variety.com/2016/film/news/ghostbusters-review-round-up-paul-feig-melissa-mccarthy-kristen-wiig-1201811470/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="reviews2">{{cite news |title='Ghostbusters': What the Critics Are Saying |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ghostbusters-what-critics-are-saying-909632 |accessdate=2016-07-11 |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2016-07-11 |archive-date=2021-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212020750/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ghostbusters-what-critics-are-saying-909632 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="reviews3">{{cite news|last=Quinn|first=Karl|url=http://www.cleveland.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2015/08/fantastic_four_reboot_may_be_t.html|title=Ghostbusters: Paul Feig, Melissa McCarthy, Kristen Wiig get mixed reviews|website=theage.com.au|date=2016-07-10|accessdate=2016-07-11|archive-date=2019-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190204231103/https://www.cleveland.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2015/08/fantastic_four_reboot_may_be_t.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]影評人新鮮度73%，但觀眾評價僅49%，基於392條評論，平均分為6.5/10<ref name="RT">{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ghostbusters_2016/ |title=Ghostbusters (2016) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2016-07-11 |archive-date=2015-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151201041827/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ghostbusters_2016/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分60<ref name="Meta">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/ghostbusters-2016 |title=Ghostbusters reviews |website=Metacritic |accessdate=2016-07-11 |archive-date=2021-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524162344/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/ghostbusters-2016 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
在美國和加拿大，《魔鬼剋星》預計於首映週末能從3700間戲院中獲得4000萬至5000萬美元的票房<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ghostbusters-tracking-40m-50m-us-905913|title='Ghostbusters' Tracking for $40M-$50M U.S. Debut|author=Pamela McClintock|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2016-06-23|accessdate=2016-06-26|archive-date=2020-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217134519/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ghostbusters-tracking-40m-50m-us-905913|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國首映週末開出4600萬美元的票房，只取得當週票房排名亞軍，第二週票房慘跌，只排名第五。

最終本片以1.44億美元的預算取得全球2.24億美元的票房，但在合併計算製作，營運及宣傳等其他綜合成本後，慘賠7000萬美元。

